==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: magnetic force
<hw>magnetic force</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The force caused by a
magnetic field, a force which affects objects having a magnetic field
and objects in which a magnetic field can be induced, such as
ferromagnetic substances; a magnetic force manifests itself as an
attraction for iron. It is associated with electric currents and moving
charged paticles as well as permanent magnets.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> magnetism, magnetic attraction.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>magnetic head</ent>⟦br⟧
